oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Class ring of Sadie Priscilla Jones
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: This class ring was given to Sadie Priscilla Jones by her future husband, Mike Glynn, when she was in high school in Jackson, Tennessee. She later married him after World War, 1914-1918. He was a farmer and only went to school through the 6th grade. He served in the 42nd Div. during the World War, 1914-1918.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: World War, 1914-1918; World War, 1914-1918 - History
